-- Bezeq Says Lawsuits Filed Against Internet, Satellite TV, Wireless Units
-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 2010-10-25T05:58:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/bezeq-says-satellite-tv-internet-wireless-units-were-sued-in-israel.html
Bezeq Israeli Telecommunication
Corp. said that lawsuits have been filed against its wireless,
Internet and satellite television units. It said that the units
were studying the suits and could not assess the chances of
their success. Bezeq made the announcement to the Tel Aviv Stock
Exchange late yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gwen Ackerman in Jerusalem at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
